OL,4,G1650FLove Nature
OL,5,     GThe greater horseshoe bat was
OL,6,     Gonce widespread in the UK but due
OL,7,     Gto habitat loss their numbers
OL,8,     Gplummeted. The Vincent Wildlife
OL,9,     GTrust look after around 50% of
OL,10,     Gthe UK's population.
OL,11,G1700F5 News with Dan Walker
OL,12,     GJoin Dan Walker and the team for
OL,13,     Gthe news that matters to you.
OL,14,G1800FSusan Calman's Summer by the Sea
OL,15,     GIn Bournemouth, Susan takes a
OL,16,     Gbeachside train ride, boards a
OL,17,     Gferry to see impressive beach
OL,18,     Ghuts, visits a Victorian treasure
OL,19,     Gtrove and meets Gareth Malone for
OL,20,     Ga game of Jenga.
